The TDD exercise is complete. All 9 tests implemented and passing:

1. Empty grid → empty grid
2. Single cell dies (underpopulation)
3. Two cells die (underpopulation)
4. Live cell with 2 neighbours survives
5. Live cell with 3 neighbours survives
6. Live cell with 4+ neighbours dies (overpopulation)
7. Dead cell with exactly 3 neighbours born (reproduction)
8. Blinker oscillator (vertical → horizontal)
9. Block still life (unchanged)
